dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:38:05.000Z","msg":"快<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e52436af577b23af596001d5933e6ff5ca7443","tid":927451,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:41:02.000Z","msg":"其實美帝有冇考慮每個州喺WTO開一個會籍？<br />\n支那賊匪入到嘅世界組織就成日用3個會籍玩嘢 咁美國每個州又點解唔得？"},{"pid":"ea25ce3f2566897a5bff08109c08530cedac8693","tid":927451,"uid":5489,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e7249c83b13ad24052daac4fa754fb8650952ce4","tid":927451,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:31:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:41:41.000Z","msg":"打柒邊個？<br />\n係石岡射核彈去美國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a6d536f1aaa1a3659cb8c0812b9a810e33aa5d","tid":927451,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:45:04.000Z","msg":"美英兩國首先要嚴禁霍英東後人踏足美國及英國本土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}